To start the game, enter the file org.example/console/Main.java
and press 'Run Main'

For each question, type the number of your answer and press ENTER

Game Steps :
- Type your name and press enter.
- The HOUSE, the PET and the WAND of the player are set randomly
- If you want to start the game, type 1
- If you want to leave the game, type 2
- If you typed 1, the game start.

LEVEL PARTICULARITIES
-LEVEL1 :
Choose an object and throw it at the troll using Wingardium leviosa
Each object has a "weight" attribute. Therefore, they have a different impact.
You can throw maximum 8 objects on the troll, so choose the heaviest ones

-LEVEL2 :
